subdomain enumeration and gathering for bug bounty
feel free to fork and contribute
Created by Garrett.




This script requires the tool ffuf the best way to get it if you have Go compiler installed is through the github at https://github.com/ffuf/ffuf if not there are precompiled binaries on the downloads page (as of 11/27 fuff is not fully integrated)

USAGE*

scan.sh <domain>


You can created an alias to the file for easy use 

EX: alias scan="bash ~/Desktop/scripts/scan.sh"
